title: The Adventures of Hajji Baba [1954 - USA] multi audio
description:
The Adventures of Hajji Baba (1954 - USA)

Action / Adventure / Romance
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0046683/


One very mean princess. A trick horse. Arab barbers. Harem girls. Camels, donkeys and lots of horses. Desert sands, rugged mountains, oasis. Colourful wardrobes of many brilliant hues. All of this set to the wonderful and haunting lyrics of Nat King Cole. In a case of mistaken identities, lowly barber Hajji Baba finds himself escorting Princess Fakzia across the desert, and together they embark on a journey fraught with dancing girls and Caliphate guards. The Adventures of Hajji Baba is a racy, sex-soaked oasis of a film and a unique, unexpected product of 1950s cinema.
